                        class="- topic/xref "
                        href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">19.507</xref>
               </ph>(f)(2), substitute the following paragraph (a) for paragraph (a) of the basic clause:</p>
            <p class="- topic/p " id="id203KD05A0PM" outputclass="List1">(a) The Contracting Officer will set aside orders for the small business concerns identified in <xref base="i1101771"
                     class="- topic/xref "
                     href="19.000.dita#FAR_19_000"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">19.000</xref>(a)(3) when the conditions of FAR <xref base="i1100762"
                     class="- topic/xref "
                     href="19.502-2.dita#FAR_19_502_2"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">19.502-2</xref> and the specific program eligibility requirements are met, as applicable.</p>
